string.name: permission_xiaoai_desc
string.Data: Mi AI will collect your voice recordings and device ID to transcribe audio and create voice notes. Learn more in Mi AI Privacy Policy.

string.name: permission_xiaoai_desc_m
string.Data: In order to provide speech-to-text transcription services, Mi AI needs to collect audio input and your device IMEI. Read and agree to the Notes Third Party Data Sharing Statement before you continue. You can also learn more by reading the Mi AI Privacy Policy.

string.name: permission_xiaoai_desc_new
string.Data: In order to provide speech-to-text transcription services, Mi AI needs to collect audio input and your device ID, which is randomly generated. Read and agree to our Notes Third Party Data Sharing Statement before you continue. You can also learn more by reading the Mi AI Privacy Policy.
